title: Google has an ‘Enhanced Safe Browsing’ feature. Should you use it?
description: Google's extra security protections from online scams are good, but they come with privacy trade-offs.

title: Hong Kong court to rule if Google, Meta must censor unofficial anthem
description: If a judge grants the government's request, global tech companies will have to ensure they do not distribute "Glory to Hong Kong" — or risk punishment.

title: Top tech firms sign White House pledge to identify AI-generated images
description: Google and the maker of ChatGPT are among the seven companies that signed onto the voluntary safety commitments.
